original_name: ATSN TV: American Trigger Sports Network Television
plot: ATSN TV covers exciting trigger sports competitions in rifle, pistol, shotgun, 3-gun, archery and more, while host, James B. Towle, shoots straight on burning gun issues with a variety of distinguished guests and top shooters.
